=head1 DESCRIPTION

The model deployment settings for the SageMaker Canvas application.

In order to enable model deployment for Canvas, the SageMaker Domain's
or user profile's Amazon Web Services IAM execution role must have the
C<AmazonSageMakerCanvasDirectDeployAccess> policy attached. You can
also turn on model deployment permissions through the SageMaker
Domain's or user profile's settings in the SageMaker console.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Status => Str

Describes whether model deployment permissions are enabled or disabled
in the Canvas application.



